# Laravel Socialite

## When to use

- Configuring OAuth social authentication (login with GitHub, Google, Facebook, etc.)
- Setting up multi-provider social login with dynamic controller
- Linking social accounts to existing users (social_accounts table)
- Configuring access scopes, Slack bot tokens, stateless auth
- Testing OAuth flows with Socialite::fake()
- Community providers (Apple, Discord, Twitch, Microsoft, etc.)

## Keywords

`socialite oauth social login github google facebook apple linkedin slack provider authentication callback`
